text: Metodi Zarev (born 8 May 1945) is a Bulgarian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 78 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Bulgaria Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Sofia
